headline: Is It Too Late to Revisit Boeing After Its 2025 Share Price Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Boeing at around $206 is still a comeback story worth paying up for, or if the market has already priced in the recovery, you are in the right place. The stock is up 10.6% over the last week, 6.0% over the past month, and has climbed 20.0% year to date and 31.3% over the last year, even though the 5 year return is still a negative 9.8%. Those moves have come as investors refocus on Boeing's role in global aircraft demand and the long term replacement cycle for...

headline: Stocks Pause Ahead of Fed Decision on Rates
summary: The stock market was struggling to hold onto even modest gains on Tuesday. The Dow was down 111 points, or 0.2%. The S&P 500 was up just 0.1%. The Nasdaq Composite was up 0.2%. Though a slim majority of stocks in the S&P 500 were up on the day, market breadth was slipping.
